snippet.title: Super Spelling Ducks Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
🕹️WISHLIST ON STEAM HERE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2719850/Super_Spelling_Ducks/

Push blocks, build words, and duck with your friends. Stack and endure curses to buy upgrades and improve your chances in this action word roguelike. Quack, waddle, and unleash the chaos of ducks!

🦆 Like the ducks? Support the game and the developer by adorning yourself with ducks! https://www.redbubble.com/people/skylegames/shop

How can I keep up to date?

🥏 Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/dGH5WbPCbG
🗒️ Follow the developer on Twitter: https://twitter.com/skylegames

Super Spelling Ducks is made by SKYLE Games, with music by Gary Clinton: https://www.garyclinton.com/
